messages.content: What features does ComfyUI-CUP provide in relation to the ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node?
ComfyUI-CUP provides a ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node thumbnail service that depends on ComfyUI-Studio, specifies InputImage/SaveImage Nodes, and offers a node-diff/queue service.
What is the installation process for ComfyUI-CUP?
To install ComfyUI-CUP, navigate to the ComfyUI/custom_nodes directory and clone the repository from the GitHub link using the command `git clone https://github.com/AIGODLIKE/ComfyUI-CUP.git`.
For which project is this repo intended to be used?
This repo is intended to be used for [ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node](https://github.com/AIGODLIKE/ComfyUI-BlenderAI-node) and not for any web-end nodes.
Does ComfyUI-CUP provide nodes for web-end?
No, this repo does not provide any nodes for web-end.
